data.description: Excellent chance to own a 2 bedroom 2 bath unit with huge picture windows in prime Buckhead location. Modern stainless steel kitchen appliances and laundry in the apartment. Large bedrooms with walk-in closets. Great layout with lots of natural light! 24-hour concierge and security, key-card access to the building, fully updated elevators, pool and gym, covered patio on the same floor, sundecks, gas grills, club rooms W/kitchen, vending machines. Two assigned parking spots in gated parking area Level C and lots of guest parking. Additional spacious storage unit included with the sale. HOA covers electricity, water, gas, trash, exterior maintenance, and all the amenities including the wonderful dog park. Publix, Walgreens, restaurants, stores, the Duck Pond with its 7.5 acres of nature, and the highly-regarded Rivers Elementary are only a walk away. Easy access to highways, buses, and MARTA's Lindbergh Station. Convenience galore!!
